<div data-pencil-name="Hero" class="box-border w-full  shrink-0 flex flex-col gap-[24px] p-[80px_160px] justify-center items-center bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat h-auto min-h-[560px]" style="background-image:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(30,58,138,0.82) 0%,rgba(15,36,71,0.88) 100%),url('/images/w5rYCp.png')"
    >
      <div
        data-pencil-name="Eyebrow"
        class="text-[16px]/[normal] box-border text-[#FFFFFF] font-['Space_Grotesk',system-ui,sans-serif] font-semibold tracking-[2px] text-left [white-space:nowrap]"
      >
        ДАЛАЙД ГАРЦГҮЙ ХӨГЖИЖ БУЙ ОРНУУДЫН
      </div>
      <div
        data-pencil-name="Headline"
        class="text-[52px]/[57px] box-border w-[900px] text-[#FFFFFF] font-['Space_Grotesk',system-ui,sans-serif] font-bold text-center"
      >
        ОЛОН УЛСЫН СУДАЛГААНЫ ТӨВ
      </div>
      <div
        data-pencil-name="Body"
        class="text-[16px]/[26px] box-border w-[800px] text-[#FFFFFF] font-['Space_Grotesk',system-ui,sans-serif] font-normal text-center"
      >
        Олон улсын судалгааны төв нь далайд гарцгүй хөгжиж буй орнуудын тогтвортой хөгжил, худалдаа,
        дэд бүтцийн холболтыг дэмжихэд чиглэгдсэн бодлогын судалгаа, мэдээллийн төв байх бөгөөд
        гишүүн орнууд болон олон улсын хамтрагчидтай хамтран ажилладаг.
      </div>
      <div
        data-pencil-name="CTA"
        class="box-border w-fit h-[48px] shrink-0 flex flex-row gap-0 p-[0px_32px] justify-center items-center bg-[#FFFFFF] rounded-[999px]"
      >
        <div
          data-pencil-name="CTA Label"
          class="text-[14px]/[normal] box-border text-[#1E3A8A] font-['Space_Grotesk',system-ui,sans-serif] font-semibold text-left [white-space:nowrap]"
        >
          Дэлгэрэнгүй
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        data-pencil-name="Controls"
        class="box-border w-full h-fit shrink-0 flex flex-row gap-0 justify-between items-start"
      >
        <button
          data-pencil-name="Prev"
          aria-label="Previous slide"
          class="box-border w-[40px] shrink-0 h-[40px] flex flex-row gap-0 justify-center items-center bg-[#ffffff33] hover:bg-[#ffffff55] rounded-[20px] transition-colors"
        >
          <span class="block w-0 h-0 border-r-[8px] border-r-white border-t-[5px] border-t-transparent border-b-[5px] border-b-transparent"></span>
        </button>
        <div
          data-pencil-name="Dots"
          class="box-border w-fit shrink-0 h-fit flex flex-row gap-[8px] justify-start items-center"
        >
          <button
            data-pencil-name="Dot 1"
            data-index="0"
            aria-label="Go to slide 1"
            class="hero-dot box-border w-[8px] shrink-0 h-[8px] bg-[#FFFFFF] rounded-full"
          ></button>
          <button
            data-pencil-name="Dot 2"
            data-index="1"
            aria-label="Go to slide 2"
            class="hero-dot box-border w-[6px] shrink-0 h-[6px] bg-[#ffffff66] rounded-full"
          ></button>
          <button
            data-pencil-name="Dot 3"
            data-index="2"
            aria-label="Go to slide 3"
            class="hero-dot box-border w-[6px] shrink-0 h-[6px] bg-[#ffffff66] rounded-full"
          ></button>
        </div>
        <button
          data-pencil-name="Next"
          aria-label="Next slide"
          class="box-border w-[40px] shrink-0 h-[40px] flex flex-row gap-0 justify-center items-center bg-[#ffffff33] hover:bg-[#ffffff55] rounded-[20px] transition-colors"
        >
          <span class="block w-0 h-0 border-l-[8px] border-l-white border-t-[5px] border-t-transparent border-b-[5px] border-b-transparent"></span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>